<topic id='business_definition_maternity_episode.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Maternity Episode - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_group">ACTIVITY GROUP</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 is a period of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_antenatal">Antenatal</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_labour_and_delivery">Labour and Delivery</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_postnatal">Postnatal</xref>
 care.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 may be associated with 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_fetus_episode">Fetus Episodes</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spells</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_labour_and_delivery">Labour and Deliveries</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_domiciliary_visit">Maternity Domiciliary Visits</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_midwife_episode">Midwife Episodes</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 will end:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
following discharge from 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_service">Maternity Services</xref>
 for the mother;                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
either following discharge from 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_maternity_service">Maternity Services</xref>
 or discharge from a 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_neonatal_unit">Neonatal Unit</xref>
 for a baby, whichever is later.                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
